Package: plateQC
Title: High-Throughput Screening Plate Quality Control with NRFE Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Aleksandr", "Ianevski", , "aleksandr.ianevski@helsinki.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7780-482X"))
Description: A comprehensive tool for analyzing high-throughput screening plate data 
    with advanced quality control metrics, including the Normalized Residual Fit Error 
    (NRFE). The package provides functions for processing plate data, fitting 
    dose-response curves, and calculating various quality control metrics including 
    Z-factor, SSMD, and NRFE.
